
Section 8 - tell_player

#include <sys.h>
#include <hear.h>

tell_player(player,actor,actee,type,message)

object player,actor,actee;
int type;
string message;

This tells the message 'message' to the specified player, by calling
the function hear() on the specified player.

See Also: hear(9), tell_room(8), tell_room_except(8), tell_room_except2(8)

